overview:
Chad Henning is a former Ebay Powerseller with large scale sales in the late 2000’s. He has since fallen from grace having lost his business and continues to be a low level Ebay seller.

Primarily focused now on Internet marketing and contributing to Youtube he continues to push himself forward. He is nowhere near the success he once had but says “Having the chance to make so much money in the past and then lose it all gave me a better understanding of who I am and what I want to be about.”

He is currently working a low paying job while he tries for a comeback but after 3 years out of the lime light his time may have passed.
